show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा

show.description: Anjali, a top scientist at ISO, secretly worships the dark deity Kaal Asur and sacrifices children in his name. But her obsession isn’t limited to the occult — she uses blood rituals, blame games, and black magic to possess her “soul-mate,” Vikram Sharma, a fellow Mars mission scientist. Just when everything seems within her grasp, another brilliant scientist, Priya, enters the scene. Will she become the final obstacle in Anjali’s twisted path, or the key to Vikram’s salvation?
